lib\features\profile\data\data_source\firebase_storage_services.dart
    helper functions to deal with firebase storage

lib\features\profile\data\models\user_model.dart
    contain all the user data that we need in the profile view (userName, email, phone, profileURL, uId)

lib\features\profile\data\repo_implementation\profile_repo_impl.dart
lib\features\profile\domain\repo_interface\profile_repo.dart
    contains fucntionalities of profile view (updateImage, getProfileData, updateProfileData, updatePassword)

lib\features\profile\presentation\views\profile_view.dart
    contains UI of profile view